# tshchemistry

This is an example API to keep track of known elements in Chemistry

## Elements Collection [/elements]

### List All Elements [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    [   
        {
            "id": 1,
            "name": "Hydrogen",
            "atomicWeight": 1,
            "atomicNumber": 1,
            "group": 1,
            "period": 1,
            "finder": "Henry Cavendish"
        },
        {
            "id": 2,
            "name": "Helium",
            "atomicWeight": 1,
            "atomicNumber": 2,
            "group": 1,
            "period": 1,
            "finder": "???"
        },
        {
