### Create a New Element [POST]

If you have discovered new element, you should use this

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "name": "Lithium",
            "atomicWeight": 1,
            "atomicNumber": 3,
            "group": 1,
            "period": 1,
            "finder": "Johan August Arfwedson"
        }
        
+ Response 204 

## Manage Elements [/elements/{id}]

+ Parameters
  + id: 1
  
  
### Fetch a single Element [GET]

You need to get one element

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "name": "Lithium",
            "atomicWeight": 1,
            "atomicNumber": 3,
            "group": 1,
            "period": 1,
            "finder": "Johan August Arfwedson"
        }

### Edit an Element [PUT]

There is a mistake in the periodic table!

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "name": "Lithium",
            "atomicWeight": 1,
            "atomicNumber": 3,
            "group": 1,
